oakcurric:priorknowledge-3855-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils know that all games have similar features of attacking and defensive play to
  either score or deny scoring opportunities respectively."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.884568Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3855-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils understand that football, netball, rugby, basketball and handball are all
  examples of invasion games with different rules."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.884586Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3855-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils are able to control and pass a ball in a variety of ways."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.884593Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3855-4
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils show a willingness to try new activities and focus on improving their
  skills."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.884598Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3856-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils know that good body control and an awareness of safety is essential and
  includes always working within personal capabilities."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.901517Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3856-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils understand that improving individual skills requires focus and dedication to
  practice."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.901532Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3856-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils are able to perform basic forms of locomotion and balances with good body
  form."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.901539Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3856-4
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils show an awareness of the dedication and hours required to see significant
  improvements in movement quality, control and fluency."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.901545Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3857-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils know how to use dance as an effective means of communicating ideas."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.913768Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3857-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils understand a variety of techniques to respond to a stimuli."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.913788Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3857-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils are able to develop motifs and use them effectively to build short dance
  routines."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.913795Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3857-4
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils show an awareness of a wide range of physical, choreographic and analytical
  skills concurrently."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.913801Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3859-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils know that taking part in fitness activities can have a positive impact on
  their health."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.932429Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3859-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils understand that different people have different fitness levels."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.932448Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3859-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils are able to perform basic exercises to improve fitness such as running or
  bodyweight exercises."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.932454Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3859-4
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils show ways to adapt exercise to suit their needs and motivations."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.932460Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3858-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils know the importance of using logical and creative thinking to solve
  problems."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.954897Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3858-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils understand that in order to improve, we need to reflect on both the positives
  and negatives of our performance."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.954916Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3858-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils are able to work under pressure, often against the clock."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.954923Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3858-4
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils show patience and resilience when faced with a challenging task."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:23.954929Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3026-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils can use dance as an effective means of communicating ideas."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.953552Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3026-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils can refine the communication of an idea by applying space, dynamics,
  relationships or stylistic features."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.953564Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3026-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils can use a variety of techniques to respond to a stimuli."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.953569Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3026-4
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils can vary or develop motifs and use them effectively to build short dances
  alone or in a group."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.953574Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3026-5
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils can utilise a wide range of physical, choreographic and analytical skills
  concurrently."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.953578Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3046-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label "Pupils know a variety of ways to mark an opposition."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.985761Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3046-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils understand the importance of maintaining possession and also invading
  territory to create space to score in the goal."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.985773Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3046-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils are able to catch and pass the ball to a teammate over a range of distances
  and in different ways to avoid a defender."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.985780Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3046-4
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils show the show the ability to apply rules in invasion games and can officiate
  small sided games fairly."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.985785Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3042-1
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils know how to perform a range of technical skills such as passing, receiving
  and shooting."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.988105Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3042-2
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils understand how to apply a range of attacking and defensive principles to
  create or close down space respectively.."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.988118Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:priorknowledge-3042-3
  a curric:PriorKnowledgeRequirement ;
  rdfs:label """Pupils are able to work well as a team to apply different tactics in a game
  situation to keep/gain possession and create/deny point scoring opportunities.."""@en ;
