  scenarios."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:41.064628Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:pupillessonoutcome-lesson-29765
  a curric:PupilLessonOutcome ;
  rdfs:label "I can apply the best technique for jumping in different ways."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:41.064660Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:pupillessonoutcome-lesson-29770
  a curric:PupilLessonOutcome ;
  rdfs:label "I can use actions, space and dynamics to explore a motif."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:41.064684Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:pupillessonoutcome-lesson-29778
  a curric:PupilLessonOutcome ;
  rdfs:label """I can complete a flow training session to improve flexibility, mobility and
  mindfulness."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:41.064725Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:pupillessonoutcome-lesson-29767
  a curric:PupilLessonOutcome ;
  rdfs:label "I can throw with coordination and accuracy from both hands in a variety of ways."@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:41.064757Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:pupillessonoutcome-lesson-29774
  a curric:PupilLessonOutcome ;
  rdfs:label """I can break down a task to solve a problem, then reflect on my performance
  afterwards."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:41.064775Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:pupillessonoutcome-lesson-29777
  a curric:PupilLessonOutcome ;
  rdfs:label """I can complete a sustained, continuous training session at a steady-state,
  sub-maximal level to develop cardiovascular endurance."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:41.064791Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:pupillessonoutcome-lesson-29768
  a curric:PupilLessonOutcome ;
